// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0652 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: eda94e58-8b9b-5a86-a72e-f064a9828320

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:24.04*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
